        description: "PEM contents of the machine-account client certificate (mutual TLS). ONE certificate authenticates every German region feed below — set it once, then just add each region's subscription id. Recommended: generate your own keypair with `openssl req -x509 -newkey rsa:4096 -nodes -days 825 -keyout mobilithek.key.pem -out mobilithek.cert.pem -subj \"/CN=openmapx-mobilithek\"`, upload mobilithek.cert.pem under the machine account's 'Zertifikat hochladen' tab (no SMS needed), then paste mobilithek.cert.pem here and mobilithek.key.pem in the next field. Alternative: convert an issued .p12 with `openssl pkcs12 -in m.p12 -clcerts -nokeys | openssl x509` (cert) and `openssl pkcs12 -in m.p12 -nocerts -nodes | openssl rsa` (key).",
